comment: Fix race condition error when installing to long paths, path folders would be deleted and recreated in time for installing files. Also support bower.json and component.json files (bower.json taking precedence)
Change multi path install to be based upon file type
Add add the ability to install to multiple paths
No need to have duplicate bower-install and bower-install.js and updated package.json so that npm can get the latest package
If property name is not existent on component.json default to property main on package.json
If component.json point to a folder, try checking for the existence of a package.json file and try to use the main property from it to create the copy instead
Fix bower dependency to be the latest
Add the ability to provide multiple sources to install
